cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DS 

The paper discusses the framework of semisupervised learning, which is a popular topic in machine learning and falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also focuses on text classification and structured prediction in NLP, which are subfields of cs.CL (Computation and Language). The use of naive Bayes, MRFs, and CRFs suggests that the paper may also fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper uses simulation studies and real-world experiments, indicating that it may also belong to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
